Helena Kallianiotes https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Helena_Kallianiotes 0 Helena Kallianiotes (born March 24, 1938) is a Greek-American film actress. In 1973, she was nominated for the Golden Globe Award for Best Supporting Actress – Motion Picture for her role as Jackie Burdette in Kansas City Bomber.
